<body id="page-top">

  <!-- Page Wrapper -->
  <div id="wrapper">

    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <% include partials/nav.ejs %>
    <!-- End of Sidebar -->

    <!-- Content Wrapper -->
    <div id="content-wrapper" class="d-flex flex-column">

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div id="content">

        <!-- Topbar -->
        <% include partials/top-nav.ejs %>

        <!-- End of Topbar -->

        <!-- Begin Page Content -->
        <div class="container-fluid">

          <!-- Page Heading -->
          <div class="d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-4">
            <h4 class="m-0 font-weight-bold text-primary">------10.10 - Threats Declaration------</h4>            
          </div>          


          <form action="/planning/threats-declaration/:user" method="POST">
            <!-- Content Row -->
          <div class="row">

            <!-- Content Column -->
            <div class="col-lg-12 mb-4">

              <!-- Engagement details Card -->
              
                <% include partials/engagementCard.ejs %>

              <!-- Additional Engagement Card-->                
              <div class="card shadow mb-4">
                <div class="card-header py-3">
                  <h6 class="m-0 font-weight-bold text-primary">Meeting Details</h6>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="engagementPartner">Engagement Partner
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="engagementPartner" name="engagementPartner">
                    </label>                    
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="meetingDate">Date
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="date" id="today" name="today" readonly>
                    </label>
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="teamMembers">Team Members
                        <textarea class="form-control form-control-sm" id="teamMembers" name="teamMembers" cols="150" rows="5"></textarea>
                    </label>                    
                    
                </div>
              </div>        


              <!--Independence Declaration Card-->
              <div class="card shadow mb-4">

                <!-- Card Header - Accordion -->
                <a href="#independenceDeclarationCard" class="d-block card-header py-3" data-toggle="collapse" role="button" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseCardExample">
                    <h6 class="m-0 font-weight-bold text-primary">INDEPENDENCE DECLARATION<br>THREATS TO INDEPENDENCE</h6>
                </a>

                <!-- Card Content - Collapse -->
                <div class="collapse" id="independenceDeclarationCard">

                  <div class="card-body">
                    I hereby wish to inform the firm that the following threats to independence have occurred:
                      
                    <div class="table-responsive">
                        <table class="table table-bordered" id="threatsTable" width="100%" cellspacing="0">
                            
                            <thead class="table-header-row">
                              <tr>
                                <th>Threat</th>
                                <th>Details</th>                                
                              </tr>
                            </thead>
                          <tbody>
                            <tr>
                              <td>Self-Interest Threat (*)</td>
                              <td contenteditable="true"></td>                                                            
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Self-Review Threat (!)</td>
                                <td contenteditable="true"></td>                                                            
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Advocacy Threat (#)</td>
                                <td contenteditable="true"></td>                                                            
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Familiarity Threat ($)</td>
                                <td contenteditable="true"></td>                                                            
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Intimidation Threat (%)</td>
                                <td contenteditable="true"></td>                                                            
                            </tr>                          

                          </tbody>
                          

                        </table>                        
                    </div>

                    <br><br>
                    * Self-Interest Threat: When a firm or member of the assurance team could benefit from a financial interest in an assurance client. 
                    <br><br>
                    ! Self-Review Threat: When a judgment from a previous assurance engagement or non-assurance engagement needs to be re-evaluated in reaching conclusions on the assurance engagement or when a member of the assurance team was previously a director or officer of the client.
                    <br><br>
                    # Advocacy Threat: Where a firm or a member of the assurance team promotes an assurance client’s position or opinion.  
                    <br><br>
                    $ Familiarity Threat: When, by virtue of a close relationship with an assurance client, its directors, officers or employees, a firm or a member of the assurance team becomes too sympathetic to the client’s interests.  
                    <br><br>
                    % Intimidation Threat: When a member of the assurance team may be deterred from acting objectively and exercising professional scepticism by threats, actual or perceived, from the directors, officers or employees of an assurance client.
                    <br><br>

                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="teamMember1">Team Member
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="teamMember1" name="teamMember1">
                    </label>                    
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="signature1">Signature
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="signature1" name="signature1" readonly>
                    </label>
                    <br>
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="teamMember2">Team Member
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="teamMember2" name="teamMember2">
                    </label>                    
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="signature2">Signature
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="signature2" name="signature2" readonly>
                    </label>
                    <br>
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="teamMember3">Team Member
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="teamMember3" name="teamMember3">
                    </label>                    
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="signature3">Signature
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="signature3" name="signature3" readonly>
                    </label>
                    <br>
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="teamMember4">Team Member
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="teamMember4" name="teamMember4">
                    </label>                    
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="signature4">Signature
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="signature4" name="signature4" readonly>
                    </label>
                    <br><br>
                    By signing this document the engagement team acknowledge that they are aware of the IFAC code and they are not aware of any transgressions thereof
                    <br><br>

                    <div class="table-responsive">
                        <table class="table table-bordered" id="decisionsTable" width="100%" cellspacing="0">
                            
                            <thead class="table-header-row">
                              <tr>
                                <th>Decision Taken</th>
                                <th>Yes</th>                                
                              </tr>
                            </thead>
                          <tbody>
                            <tr>
                              <td>Keep team member but institute safeguards</td>
                              <td contenteditable="true"></td>                                                            
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Remove team member</td>
                                <td contenteditable="true"></td>
                            </tr>                                                      
                                               
                          </tbody>
                          

                        </table>                        
                    </div>
                    
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
             



              <button class="btn btn-info btn-long" type="submit">Submit</button>
              <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-long" type="reset">Reset All Fields</button>

            </div>
            
          </div>
          </form>

        </div>
        <!-- /.container-fluid -->

      </div>
      <!-- End of Main Content -->

      <!-- Footer -->
      <% include partials/footer.ejs %>
      <!-- End of Footer -->

    </div>
    <!-- End of Content Wrapper -->

  </div>
  <!-- End of Page Wrapper -->

